<li>"<a href="/wiki/The_Thieving_Magpie" title="The Thieving Magpie" class="mw-redirect">The Thieving Magpie</a> (<a href="/wiki/Gioacchino_Rossini" title="Gioacchino Rossini" class="mw-redirect">Rossini</a>, Abridged)", A <a href="/wiki/Deutsche_Grammophon" title="Deutsche Grammophon">Deutsche Grammophon</a> Recording</li>
<li>"Theme from <i>A Clockwork Orange</i> (Beethoviana)", Wendy Carlos</li>
<li>"Ninth Symphony, Second Movement (Abridged)", A Deutsche Grammophon Recording conducted by <a href="/wiki/Ferenc_Fricsay" title="Ferenc Fricsay">Ferenc Fricsay</a>.</li>
